<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1932-11-16T16:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1932-11-16T16:00:00-05:00" n="269" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d269">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">500.A15A4 Steering Committee/154:
                            Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The American Delegate (<persName corresp="#p_WHR1" type="from">Wilson</persName>) to the <gloss type="to">Secretary
                                    of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Geneva</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-11-16T22:00:00+01:00">November
                                    16, 1932—10 p.m.</date>
                                <lb/> [Received November 16—5:45 p.m.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>460. Referring to my 458, November 16, 7 p.m., and 459, November 16, 9
                            p.m., we are contemplating submitting to you certain suggestions
                            concerning the method of handling the situation created by the French
                            plan but prefer to await <persName corresp="#p_SSJ1">Simon</persName>’s
                            statement tomorrow and subsequent private conversations before bringing
                            them to your attention.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <persName corresp="#p_WHR1">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson</hi>
                                </persName>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>